The paper deals with the computation of the contour tree of a scalar field on a triangulated simplicial mesh, which is a fundamental topological structure with applications in data analysis and visualization. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories related to computational geometry (cs.CG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), graphics (cs.GR), computer vision (cs.CV), and scientific computing (cs.SI).
